==音乐录像带==
===发展===
歌曲的音乐录像带于2007年11月27日和28日在[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]''Social Hollywood''的夜店和餐厅拍摄。由先前导演过布兰妮《[[少女已过，熟女未满|少女已过，熟女未满]]》音乐录像带的韦恩·艾沙姆导演。<ref name=mtvreport>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1575195/20071128/spears_britney.jhtml|title=Britney Spears Shoots 'Piece Of Me' Video, Using Pursued-By-Paparazzi Theme|date=2007-11-28|accessdate=2010-02-10|last=Aswad|first=Jem|publisher=MTV. MTV Networks|archive-date=2009-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220143444/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1575195/20071128/spears_britney.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 英国《[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]》报道称音乐录像带花费50万美元，是布兰妮继《中你的毒》之后花费最高的音乐录像带。<ref name=dailymail>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-503097/Was-Britney-slimmed-new-video.html|title=Was Britney 'slimmed down' in new video?|date=2007-12-18|accessdate=2010-02-10|last=Reporter|first=Daily Mail|work=[[Daily_Mail|Daily Mail]]|publisher=[[Daily_Mail_and_General_Trust|Daily Mail and General Trust]]|archive-date=2013-02-27|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6EklL0eA8?url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-503097/Was-Britney-slimmed-new-video.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在音乐录像带的部分场景中，布兰妮穿着由美国设计师玛琳娜·托比纳设计的紫色缎子裙。<ref name=dress>{{cite news|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report_spears-might-bring-fame-to-little-known-designer_1139866|title=Spears might bring fame to little known designer|date=2007-12-17|accessdate=2010-02-10|last=Reporter|first=DNA|work=[[DNA_(newspaper)|DNA]]|publisher=Diligent Media Corporation|archive-date=2012-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120922124503/http://www.dnaindia.com/entertainment/report_spears-might-bring-fame-to-little-known-designer_1139866|dead-url=no}}</ref> 布兰妮被报道称因陪伴两个儿子在音乐录像带中迟到了12个小时。<ref name=mtvreport/> 艾沙姆谈到这件事时称：“她是迟到了。人们把这件事过度放大了，但她怎么能不迟到呢，试想一下当有50，60或者75或者更多的人在街上不停地围追着她的车时？这对全体拍摄成员都是漫长的一天。不夸张地说，全体拍摄成员经历了一个长度为二十小时的一天，她在这里花了6个小时拍摄。虽然她迟到了，但是到场了，说闲话的人都要踢屁股”。<ref name=tscpieceofme>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1626910/20091123/spears_britney.jhtml|title=Britney Spears Took Aim At The Media In 'Piece Of Me' Video|date=2009-11-23|accessdate=2010-02-10|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|last2=Elias|first2=Matt|publisher=MTV. MTV Networks|archive-date=2010-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100209234623/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1626910/20091123/spears_britney.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他亦解释了音乐录像带的概念：
<blockquote>
“在（这部音乐录像带）当中，我真的只想把镜头倒回到整个拍摄过程。你们可以看到她那么自信。并且，毫不夸张地说，每一个镜头的拍摄都让她更加自信，所以她对接下来的拍摄都感到无比快乐。不是那种在高处讽刺低处，但是……她自信地嘲笑了身边的那些人事。（……）在音乐录像带的一部分中，她扎高了头发，我说：‘你能为我把头发放下吗？’她就放下了头发。你将会看到我们在头发扎高和放下间不断地镜头交切。这是最后一部分。她随心而动。在结尾精心设计了舞蹈。她凭借自己做到了这些并说：‘让我们试试吧。’”<ref name=tscpieceofme/> 
</blockquote>

==现场表演==
《破碎的我》为2009年[[妮裳马戏团巡回演唱会|妮裳马戏团巡回演唱会]]表演的第2首歌曲。在布兰妮表演完歌曲《[[妮裳马戏团_(歌曲)|妮裳马戏团]]》（''Circus''）之后，布兰妮脱下了自己的红色夹克，并以马戏团团长的形象穿着由[[迪恩和丹·卡登|迪恩和丹·卡登]]设计的镶嵌[[施华洛世奇|施华洛世奇]]水晶的黑色紧身胸衣、渔网丝袜和高跟的紧系鞋带的靴子。<ref name=meta>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/fashionnews/4929913/Britney-Spears-kicks-off-Circus-world-tour-in-New-Orleans.html|title=Britney Spears kicks off Circus world tour in New Orleans|date=2009-03-02|accessdate=2009-12-11|last=Alexander|first=Hilary|first2=|last2=|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=Telegraph Media Group|archive-date=2009-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307002304/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/fashionnews/4929913/Britney-Spears-kicks-off-Circus-world-tour-in-New-Orleans.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 当烟雾环绕布兰妮时，布兰妮进入了舞台中央的笼子，《破碎的我》音乐同时响起。在表演过程中，布兰妮扮演为奴隶，试图从伴舞当中逃跑。<ref name=msnbcp>{{cite news|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/29491690/wid/17621070|title=Big Easy fans thrilled by Britney’s ‘Circus’ act|date=2009-03-04|accessdate=2009-12-16|last=Press|first=Associated|publisher=[[msnbc.com|msnbc.com]]. [[NBC_Universal|NBC Universal]] / [[Microsoft|Microsoft]]|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211142606/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/29491690/wid/17621070|dead-url=no}}</ref> 《破碎的我》亦在2011年[[蛇蝎美人巡回演唱会|蛇蝎美人巡回演唱会]]中表演。在表演完歌曲《[[三人行不行_(歌曲)|三人行不行]]》（''3''）后，布兰妮爬上一座四处浮动的小平台表演歌曲。周围的男伴舞打扮成警察模样，脱下他们的衬衫以表演[[性虐恋|性虐恋]]动作。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/britney-spears-proves-shes-still-got-it-at-femme-fatale-tour-kickoff-20110617|title=Britney Spears Proves She's Still Got It at 'Femme Fatale' Tour Kickoff|work=Rolling Stone|publisher=Jann Wenner|last=Walters|first=Barry|date=June 17, 2011|accessdate=June 17, 2011|archive-date=2011-11-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/62u3at8N1?url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/britney-spears-proves-shes-still-got-it-at-femme-fatale-tour-kickoff-20110617|dead-url=no}}</ref> 《[[好莱坞报道|好莱坞报道]]》的雪莉·霍尔珀林将《破碎的我》、《三人行不行》和《[[別讓我最後才知道|別讓我最後才知道]]》共同列为蛇蝎美人巡回演唱会最精彩的表演，称这三个表演“足具讽刺意味，（他们）在众多表演中有不多的虚饰。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/britney-spears-at-staples-center-203693|title=Britney Spears at Staples Center: Concert Review|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|last=Halperin|first=Shirley|date=June 21, 2011|accessdate=June 21, 2011|archive-date=2015-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150203174146/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/britney-spears-at-staples-center-203693|dead-url=no}}</ref> 歌曲亦是布兰妮最近的赌城驻场表演[[布兰妮：破碎的我|布兰妮：破碎的我]]表演曲目之一。<ref name=BillboardReview>{{cite web|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|title=Britney Spears' Hits-Filled 'Piece of Me' Show Opens In Las Vegas: Live Review|url=http://billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5855045/britney-spears-hits-filled-piece-of-me-show-opens-in-las-vegas|work=Billboard|date=December 28, 2013|accessdate=December 28, 2013|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914075149/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/5855045/britney-spears-hits-filled-piece-of-me-show-opens-in-las-vegas|dead-url=no}}</ref>

